{Grandmother.}
I came because I was left a small cottage which I decided to use as a 2nd home. My father and I enjoyed living here so much that we decided to stay here permanently. Being near to the hills and the beauty of the country_side and the ease of supply- ing our homely needs all helped us in our decision to stay here.
{Mother. { I was born here then I left to go to college and get married and set up a home. I came back here about five years ago because my parents were getting old. We like the area because of the country-side and having grown up here I know lots of people.
